reviews.text:
Tsui Yuen Dessert is a dessert restaurant serve with Chinese dessert.
The dessert here is great, and the restaurant is clean, tables are not packed.  The Chinese dessert is actually excellent, and nothing similar around. And their price is acceptable too. 
Just their staffs are not really friendly
The varieties of dessert goes beyond one's imagination.  Black, white, clear, yellow, creamy, watery...you name it, they have it.
Inexpensive local hk desserts. Love the texture of the steamed milk..it's not too watery compared to other desserts place
It’s the most traditional desserts in Hong Kong, managed by a few veteran of preparing these high grade delicacies in simple way
The neighborhood tong sui tong (Chinese desserts shop). Nothing grand but qualities consistent.
